### Login as demo user
# @name login
POST {{LLM_Demo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "Demo123!"
}

### List all agents
GET {{LLM_Demo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

