### List documents for the agent
GET {{LLM_Demo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/agents/{{AgentId}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### Get document details with chunks (replace DOCUMENT_ID with actual ID)
GET {{LLM_Demo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/agents/{{AgentId}}/documents/DOCUMENT_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### Search documents
GET {{LLM_Demo.Api_HostAddress}}/api/agents/{{AgentId}}/documents/search?query=разработчик
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
